properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 1 at 2:53AM PST until January 2 at 12:00PM PST by NWS Hanford CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 mph with gusts up to 40 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Tehachapi Area.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to noon PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
Gusty winds can make vehicle travel difficult, especially for
high profile vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
